processinfo.head: Processing Information note
processinfo.p: Minimal Processing has been conducted to establish basic intellectual and physical control of the material and assess immediate preservation and conservation needs. Material remains as received, in original folders and storage boxes.

separatedmaterial.head: Separated Materials
separatedmaterial.p: G. E. Uhlenbeck collection: Books (originally contained in Boxes 23-26) were relocted to the RAC Library.

scopecontent.head: Scope and Contents
scopecontent.p: This collection is comprised of: laboratory notebooks; lecture files and notes; correspondence; administrative records; awards; research files; workshop and conference files; and a variety of reprints, papers, and manuscripts.
